<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">a day</TIMEX>. Because the nature of some military assignments makes a
confirmation of the presence at duty stations difficult, if not
impossible, the recording of presence for duty and of specific
<TIMEX TYPE="TIME">hours</TIMEX> during which duty is performed <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">each day</TIMEX> is not required. This
is similar to exceptionbased <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">T&A</ENAMEX> systems explained earlier in
this document. Most active duty military <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">personnel</ENAMEX> follow
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">exceptionbased</ENAMEX> systems. However, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">superiors</ENAMEX> are expected to be aware
