<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">review</ENAMEX> and approval must be met:


<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX>.
Reports of such information and related supporting
documents must be reviewed and approved by a designated authorizing
official. The <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">official</ENAMEX> must be aware of the responsibilities he or
she is taking regarding the accuracy of the reports.


<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2</NUMEX>.
Approvals of such reports will be made at the end of the
<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">last day</TIMEX> of the pay period whenever possible. When this is not
