<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">MILITARY RESERVISTS</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">T&A</ENAMEX> controls for military reservists depend largely on the
nature of the work. If they have defined work schedules and are not
